description:
This is a 32 minute workout called '30-Minute HOME WORKOUT | No Equipment Full Body Exercise | GunjanShouts' from the channel GunjanShouts.
The workout falls under Strength/Body weight and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Disciplined Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate and Challenging.

Original workout description: Burn 375 calories in just 30 minutes by doing this - No equipment Home Workout.

Here is full body home workout video for beginners and intermediate.
Its a no equipment workout and can be easily done anywhere. It will help you in strengthening, toning and weight loss. 

Workout includes:
Arms exercises, 
legs exercises, 
chest exercises, 
belly exercises, 
love handle exercises,
core exercises,
butt exercises
pre and post workout stretching

I hope you will enjoy doing this as much as I enjoyed shooting this video for you. 🤗
